      "text": "How can software become explainable through its own knowledge graph?",
      "suggestedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Explainability improves when the public interface exposes the graph instead of hiding it. A page should show what it is, what it connects to, what evidence supports it and where its claims remain limited.",
